cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with real-time 3D human pose estimation using a single RGB camera, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also uses convolutional neural networks (CNNs) and fully-connected neural networks, which are common machine learning techniques (cs.LG and cs.AI). The paper also involves space-time skeletal model fitting, which relates to robotics (cs.RO) and graphics (cs.GR).
